{"about_the_game":"Deep Space Directive is a base-building and resource management game about expanding, exploring, building, upgrading, and of course, defending. Your directive is to generate corporate profit by expanding and exploiting the resources in the world around you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/Build_Your_Base.png?t=1738536273\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/Economy_Updated_GIF.gif?t=1738536273\" /><br>all means take the weekend! I'm a big believer in letting ideas percolate. zBuild supply chains of mines and power sources to feed your hungry smelters, factories and refineries. The corporation demands profits and rising stock prices!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/Build_Your_Economy.png?t=1738536273\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/Building_Updated__5_GIF.gif?t=1738536273\" /><br>A constant stream of fuel cells and raw resources are needed to keep your defenses functioning and your colonists fed.  Collect, refine, and process resources. Fuel cells and ore are needed for buildings and colonists need water and food. As your population grows you can support more and more buildings. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/Defend_Your_Base.png?t=1738536273\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/Combat_Updated_GIF.gif?t=1738536273\" /><br>You were sent to build mines and factories, but when you landed you discovered it wasn't that easy.  How will you defend your base? Powerful stationary towers or mobile but weaker units? Keep your energy supplies topped up before night